name: Self Similarity Variant I (Collage, Natural)
description: Created by @mathmakesart (https://mathmakes.art) on 2020-03-06. This piece is created from my "Self Similarity" original (https://www.hicetnunc.xyz/objkt/19211). It is one of ten variants on this same theme, all of which will be listed as my first single-edition sales with a price of 1.0 XTZ each. This piece and the other nine variations in this set were created with the goal of identifying unique and visually interesting 2D patterns which emerge from repeated application of a single function.
